<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11219&amp;p=128448#p128448"><![CDATA[
Tiled is a generic map editor. It takes in an image file, such as a png (can't remember if it supports other formats), of the map tiles and saves the map in XML format. You'd have to write your own to convert the XML map to a format of your choice, if one doesn't exist already.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=80">thefox</a> — Mon May 05, 2014 2:09 am</p><hr />
